":164481,"uid":93114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T16:56:10.000Z","msg":"用緊pro3 用咗三年跌過幾次都未壞<br />\n平時冇乜點保養佢<br />\n都係返工返學咁用<br />\n去旅行都係咁用<br />\n<br />\nkeyboard就買舊cyber clean嚟痴垃圾就可以<br />\n我建議個mon唔好痴mon貼 因為痴咗貼個筆尖蝕得好快<br />\n怕花就買個套<br />\n但其實都幾難花 我粗用三年都冇花<br />\n<br />\n最要小心就係條叉電<br />\n佢個頭好易斷 三年換咗三條"},{"pid":"6c15b8c356f7fea0cf9e3dd2dc1dec2fd6b7abb4","tid":164481,"uid":93114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T16:58:40.000Z","msg":"講漏咗 絨面就用個刷刷下就ok<br />\nmon可以用抹mon嗰啲水就得"},{"pid":"6f7b4bae43f8619cfac82f5048689d1f0cda34ea","tid":164481,"uid":47575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T21:37:42.000Z","msg":"我反而想知可以點清風扇..................................<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屋企有隻貓"},{"pid":"214d23c6677b2ed44e88baac1437085c48b22d90","tid":164481,"uid":83739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T22:57:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用緊pro3 用咗三年跌過幾次都未壞<br />\n平時冇乜點保養佢<br />\n都係返工返學咁用<br />\n去旅行都係咁用<br />\n<br />\nkeyboard就買舊cyber clean嚟痴垃圾就可以<br />\n我建議個mon唔好痴mon貼 因為痴咗貼個筆尖蝕得好快<br />\n怕花就買個套<br />\n但其實都幾難花 我粗用三年都冇花<br />\n<br />\n最要小心就係條叉電<br />\n佢個頭好易斷 三年換咗三條</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nmon貼唔痴我驚花mon<br />\n唔買磨沙果隻就咁高清貼都會蝕筆尖？<br />\n因為我岩岩買左隻貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外巴打keyboard啲邊位有冇皺哂皮咁？"},{"pid":"3e9c16cb7402a04c91daf7f925a729d8413d2743","tid":164481,"uid":83739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T22:59:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我反而想知可以點清風扇..................................<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屋企有隻貓</blockquote><br />\n啲貓毛kick住啲出風位？"},{"pid":"c033fb27f0ec371b15433a4ac429b8aae130e1e6","tid":164481,"uid":47575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T01:49:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我反而想知可以點清風扇..................................<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屋企有隻貓</blockquote><br />\n啲貓毛kick住啲出風位？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該係風扇度糾纏左好多<br />\n越黎越嘈<br />\n<br />\n風扇轉緊果陣打側部機<br />\n會瘋狂卡卡聲"},{"pid":"2259d06fa02fd2e81d146e98b64ac480ed346fe0","tid":164481,"uid":33655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T02:11:19.000Z","msg":"有surface pro 4 update唔到上build 1607<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇巴絲打同我一樣？"},{"pid":"8205af4a33b94b3f3b5e6a9b8639f44c04ca6547","tid":164481,"uid":83739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T03:07:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有surface pro 4 update唔到上build 1607<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇巴絲打同我一樣？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nbuild 1607 係咩意思？我睇update history 有&quot;Update for windows 10 version 1607 for x64-based systems(KB4013418)&quot;同&quot;Cumulative Update for windows 10 version 1607 for x64-based system(KB4013429) 巴打係咪update唔到呢啲？"},{"pid":"427aef8421b31b503ff14ba7b7103ffc75c0a5d0","tid":164481,"uid":93114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T03:55:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用緊pro3 用咗三年跌過幾次都未壞<br />\n平時冇乜點保養佢<br />\n都係返工返學咁用<br />\n去旅行都係咁用<br />\n<br />\nkeyboard就買舊cyber clean嚟痴垃圾就可以<br />\n我建議個mon唔好痴mon貼 因為痴咗貼個筆尖蝕得好快<br />\n怕花就買個套<br />\n但其實都幾難花 我粗用三年都冇花<br />\n<br />\n最要小心就係條叉電<br />\n佢個頭好易斷 三年換咗三條</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nmon貼唔痴我驚花mon<br />\n唔買磨沙果隻就咁高清貼都會蝕筆尖？<br />\n因為我岩岩買左隻貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外巴打keyboard啲邊位有冇皺哂皮咁？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就係高清都好快蝕<br />\nkeyboard邊位有皺呀 小小啫 唔影響功能就ok"},{"pid":"5edcfeb9e16a64bfd34cc6ac56b956d6f42944fc","tid":164481,"uid":93114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T03:57:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我反而想知可以點清風扇..................................<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屋企有隻貓</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我會用舊cyber clean塞入去<br />\n屋企人都冇個 貓毛真係唔知會點"},{"pid":"0775a607bb58809e4fa147522e0993b711bce36c","tid":164481,"uid":59529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T03:57:55.000Z","msg":"用左4半年，個筆頭就比我畫爆左"},{"pid":"f90f43df6cc68e38eb8d5e11943578439d93f4e2","tid":164481,"uid":31461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T04:05:33.000Z","msg":"Pro3 唔痴磨沙貼個moon會反光得好勁 睇得耐隻眼會好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79cc314870a9628b7ae481d4e3784dfc1cf95141","tid":164481,"uid":33655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T06:22:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有surface pro 4 update唔到上build 1607<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇巴絲打同我一樣？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nbuild 1607 係咩意思？我睇update history 有&quot;Update for windows 10 version 1607 for x64-based systems(KB4013418)&quot;同&quot;Cumulative Update for windows 10 version 1607 for x64-based system(KB4013429) 巴打係咪update唔到呢啲？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/um3vkqad\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fum3vkqad&h=7bd0ef55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔係呀 我係連1607都裝唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6286fe7da97dd26cd8dd9bafaa4a56f76254452d","tid":164481,"uid":83739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T06:44:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我反而想知可以點清風扇..................................<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屋企有隻貓</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我會用舊cyber clean塞入去<br />\n屋企人都冇個 貓毛真係唔知會點</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果cyber clean 有啲殘骸留左係入面就玩完了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a444d8782cac613a94291fee63d2f64c1d0e9937","tid":164481,"uid":83739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T06:45:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用緊pro3 用咗三年跌過幾次都未壞<br />\n平時冇乜點保養佢<br />\n都係返工返學咁用<br />\n去旅行都係咁用<br />\n<br />\nkeyboard就買舊cyber clean嚟痴垃圾就可以<br />\n我建議個mon唔好痴mon貼 因為痴咗貼個筆尖蝕得好快<br />\n怕花就買個套<br />\n但其實都幾難花 我粗用三年都冇花<br />\n<br />\n最要小心就係條叉電<br />\n佢個頭好易斷 三年換咗三條</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nmon貼唔痴我驚花mon<br />\n唔買磨沙果隻就咁高清貼都會蝕筆尖？<br />\n因為我岩岩買左隻貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外巴打keyboard啲邊位有冇皺哂皮咁？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就係高清都好快蝕<br />\nkeyboard邊位有皺呀 小小啫 唔影響功能就ok</blockquote><br />\n係咪因爲痴mon貼後sensitivity 差左要大力啲先用到支筆搞到蝕左？"},{"pid":"1a07c9c77b531ec37b14a2d85cc226d8394df6a0","tid":164481,"uid":83739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T06:52:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有surface pro 4 update唔到上build 1607<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇巴絲打同我一樣？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nbuild 1607 係咩意思？我睇update history 有&quot;Update for windows 10 version 1607 for x64-based systems(KB4013418)&quot;同&quot;Cumulative Update for windows 10 version 1607 for x64-based system(KB4013429) 巴打係咪update唔到呢啲？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/um3vkqad\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fum3vkqad&h=7bd0ef55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔係呀 我係連1607都裝唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ngoogle話關xblSave事 有冇試過搞搞佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/tech/gxe48m.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Ftech%2Fgxe48m.html&d=qlseXWlRX%2BAJHWkEdqgF5f1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=cc64ff7d\" target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/tech/gxe48m.html</a>"},{"pid":"594127bc67b0b7e90a3c233a2056fe5e9f5b0244","tid":164481,"uid":9055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T06:59:45.000Z","msg":"我部Pro3 用左2年半到, 而家唔差住電用得20分鐘，有冇人知可以點搞...?"},{"pid":"f4dde948ac827e2bfd186b7174a5be82771b3cb0","tid":164481,"uid":83739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T09:44:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我部Pro3 用左2年半到, 而家唔差住電用得20分鐘，有冇人知可以點搞...?</blockquote><br />\n啲電得返85%或以下 可以打去Microsoft 可以換部新<br />\n不過過左保養就要加錢<br />\n我之前部surface pro3 倒瀉水打左柴 過左保養<br />\n打電話去問佢 加4500可換部全新（佢話全新<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n如果只係得電既問題應該唔洗咁貴<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.microsoft.com/surface/zh-hk/support/warranty-service-and-recovery/surface-warranty\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.microsoft.com%2Fsurface%2Fzh-hk%2Fsupport%2Fwarranty-service-and-recovery%2Fsurface-warranty&d=qlseXWlRX%2BAJHWkEdqgF5f1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=e4144c67\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.microsoft.com/surface/zh-hk/support/warranty-service-and-recovery/surface-warranty</a>"},{"pid":"7b048f13147c2485773f051fd137e55d5d8c0e73","tid":164481,"uid":83739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T10:36:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7f18ce5583e0fd720e844b6a399407ac7370ef1","tid":164481,"uid":83739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T12:08:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa8822e5e5abc482a52ba9b86cf4bc55aba7860e","tid":164481,"uid":93114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T17:21:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我反而想知可以點清風扇..................................<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屋企有隻貓</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我會用舊cyber clean塞入去<br />\n屋企人都冇個 貓毛真係唔知會點</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果cyber clean 有啲殘骸留左係入面就玩完了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n三年嚟都係咁 都冇事喎 <br />\n未玩完 有冇cyber clean喺入面就唔清楚"},{"pid":"34179acbf4b587b2eff9f13a3547779b8e9674cc","tid":164481,"uid":93114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T17:22:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用緊pro3 用咗三年跌過幾次都未壞<br />\n平時冇乜點保養佢<br />\n都係返工返學咁用<br />\n去旅行都係咁用<br />\n<br />\nkeyboard就買舊cyber clean嚟痴垃圾就可以<br />\n我建議個mon唔好痴mon貼 因為痴咗貼個筆尖蝕得好快<br />\n怕花就買個套<br />\n但其實都幾難花 我粗用三年都冇花<br />\n<br />\n最要小心就係條叉電<br />\n佢個頭好易斷 三年換咗三條</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nmon貼唔痴我驚花mon<br />\n唔買磨沙果隻就咁高清貼都會蝕筆尖？<br />\n因為我岩岩買左隻貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外巴打keyboard啲邊位有冇皺哂皮咁？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就係高清都好快蝕<br />\nkeyboard邊位有皺呀 小小啫 唔影響功能就ok</blockquote><br />\n係咪因爲痴mon貼後sensitivity 差左要大力啲先用到支筆搞到蝕左？</blockquote><br />\n我覺得唔關sensitivity事 因為佢都已經非常sensitive<br />\n可能係mon貼冇個mon咁滑"},{"pid":"855c7fa7522770853df9fee952f8efcf1a46641a","tid":164481,"uid":93114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T17:23:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我部Pro3 用左2年半到, 而家唔差住電用得20分鐘，有冇人知可以點搞...?</blockquote><br />\n去Microsoft買保養 好似有得淨係保舊電"},{"pid":"0d29737b4063054e377b61de54ee117ec490a028","tid":164481,"uid":83739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T00:10:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2807fbe32ffcab26391ca1491a4c0bb446cadc9c","tid":164481,"uid":83739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T05:56:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9d94d1be7af39287884a368a7dbffb49d3610c0","tid":164481,"uid":83739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T11:45:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7514b4e1256fe7eb0e7f89324899e6a6e5444e1","tid":164481,"uid":232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T12:12:07.000Z","msg":"Sp4 如果用支筆篤個virtual keyboard<br />\n有時篤一下會出兩個字<br />\n有冇人都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f73555a3fdda3b88d2474b554402f5ef7f4512cd","tid":164481,"uid":19947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T14:46:34.000Z","msg":"有無方法解決解像度高 令到啲程式icon變得超細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /